Unwrap project:

sudo apt-get install python-dev
sudo apt-get install libevent-dev
sudo apt-get install libxml2 libxslt

git clone git://github.com/alexkos/picker.git
pip install -r requirements.txt

Create settings.py:

In database user:admin, pass:password, name:picker

secret_keys = g56wm7m@aj)4^&amp;2dua!@t21_)b_w_cf8c@p7ltezjglx#$95o@
